# Flycast Design Guidelines

**Overall feel:** Light, clean, airport-inspired. Departure boards meet modern web design. Every element earns its space.

**Colors:**
- Background: white or very light gray (#FAFAFA)
- Text: dark gray/near-black (#1A1A1A)
- Accent: airport blue (#0066CC) or warm amber (#F59E0B)
- Cards: white with subtle border or shadow

**Typography:**
- Font: Inter or Geist Sans
- Messages: at least 18px on mobile (large, readable)
- Timestamps: smaller, muted text

**Layout:**
- Mobile-first responsive
- Single column, full-width message cards
- Admin: compose area sticky at top on desktop

**Animations:**
- New messages: slide in from top with subtle fade
- Keep minimal and smooth — no flashy transitions

**Empty state:** "No announcements yet. Stay tuned." with a subtle plane icon.
